comment.value: Authors: Justin Pead; Heather Wimberley; Noah Havik; Kelvin Yankey
Be aware of current loading the volatge input protection circuit
Schottky diodes can be replaced with a p-channel mosfet configuration
Chips used here are EEPROM and FTDI chip (convert between USB connector and UART)
External Pins connect to STM325f0 Discovery Board
I2C is being used to connect EEPROM to microcontroller
